Users Outside the United States
Our Services are hosted in the United States, governed by United States law, and targeted to individuals located in the United States.  If you are using our Services from outside the United States, please be aware that your information may be transferred to, stored and processed in the United States where our servers are located, and our central database is operated. The data protection and other laws of the United States and other countries might not be as comprehensive as, or just different from, those in your country. By using our Services, you consent to your information being transferred to our facilities and to the facilities of those third parties with whom we disclose it as described in this Privacy Policy.
