Our Policy
This Privacy Policy describes the privacy practices of Ad Hoc Labs, Inc. (“
Ad Hoc Labs
”, “we”, “us” and/or “our”) with respect to our use and disclosure of the information that we collect about users of the Burner mobile application, the website, burnerapp.com, the Firewall mobile application, related services, any other services where the Privacy Policy is shown, and any other interactions we may have with you online and offline (collectively, our “
Services
”).
Before you use or submit any information through or in connection with our Services, please carefully review this Privacy Policy. By using any part of our Services, you understand that your information will be collected, used, and disclosed as outlined in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to this Privacy Policy, please do not use our Services.
